  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Kusoku.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are able to manifest clones from your sheer speed. You are only able to summon one clone at a time. Clones you cast have HP equal to your dexterity score at the time of casting. The clone's AC is equal to your Taijutsu save DC. This clone spawns in a space within 5 feet of you that can hold it. You cannot directly control this clone. When you make an unarmed attack, weapon attack, or cast a taijutsu with the wind release keyword, your clone casts the same jutsu targeting a creature within 5 feet of your target. Attacks from your clone compare your original attack result to their targets AC. The Clone always moves with you, staying within 5 feet of you and is unable to be forcefully pulled away from you. The clone can benefit from any Kōsoku feature that you have active.</p>",
